WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.900 align:middle line:90%


00:00:01.900 --> 00:00:04.210 align:middle line:90%
>> Hello I'm Chantel Westerman.

00:00:04.210 --> 00:00:06.500 align:middle line:84%
One of the best parts
of the Wisdom Workshops

00:00:06.500 --> 00:00:08.740 align:middle line:84%
are the up close and
personal conversations

00:00:08.740 --> 00:00:10.810 align:middle line:84%
with the leading
practitioners and authors

00:00:10.810 --> 00:00:12.460 align:middle line:90%
in the holistic field.

00:00:12.460 --> 00:00:14.710 align:middle line:84%
This gives all of
us an opportunity

00:00:14.710 --> 00:00:16.960 align:middle line:84%
to know these people
just a little bit better.

00:00:16.960 --> 00:00:21.962 align:middle line:84%
So join me as they share
their wisdom with us.

00:00:21.962 --> 00:00:23.444 align:middle line:90%
